{"id": "26520", "post": "<div class=\"post-26520 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-editorial tag-buyshared tag-buyvm tag-cpanel tag-shared-hosting\" id=\"post-26520\"><h2 class=\"storytitle\"><a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/blog/buyvm-puts-new-buyshared-signups-on-pause/\" rel=\"bookmark\">BuyVM Puts New BuyShared Signups on Pause</a></h2><div class=\"meta\"><img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"/media/icons/tag_green.png\" data-src=\"/media/icons/tag_green.png\" alt=\"Tags: \" class=\"litespeed-loaded\" data-was-processed=\"true\"> <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/buyshared/\" rel=\"tag\">buyshared</a>, <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/buyvm/\" rel=\"tag\">buyvm</a>, <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/cpanel/\" rel=\"tag\">cpanel</a>, <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/shared-hosting/\" rel=\"tag\">shared hosting</a> <img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"https://lowendbox.com/media/icons/calendar.png\" data-src=\"https://lowendbox.com/media/icons/calendar.png\" alt=\"Date/Time: \" class=\"litespeed-loaded\" data-was-processed=\"true\"> March 8, 2021 @ 7:20 pm, by raindog308</div><div class=\"storycontent tablelook\"><p><img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/buyvm_300.png.webp\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"size-full wp-image-26521 alignright litespeed-loaded\" data-src=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/buyvm_300.png.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" align=\"right\" hspace=\"20\" data-srcset=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/buyvm_300.png.webp 300w, https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/buyvm_300-150x150.png.webp 150w\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" srcset=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/buyvm_300.png.webp 300w, https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/buyvm_300-150x150.png.webp 150w\" data-was-processed=\"true\">As <a href=\"https://www.lowendtalk.com/discussion/170316/buyshared-net-no-more\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">discussed on LowEndTalk,</a> community favorite <a href=\"https://www.buyvm.net\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">BuyVM</a> has decided to pause new signups for <a href=\"https://www.buyshared.net\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">BuyShared</a>, its shared-hosting brand for 2021.&nbsp; According to @Francisco (BuyVM\u2019s owner), they are focusing on the VM hosting side of the house.</p><p><a href=\"https://www.buyshared.net/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">BuyShared</a> is still in operation, upgrades/downgrades are possible, and they are providing full support, so if you\u2019re a happy <a href=\"https://www.buyshared.net/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">BuyShared</a> user today, you can continue to be a happy <a href=\"https://www.buyshared.net/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">BuyShared</a> user tomorrow.&nbsp; If you\u2019re not a <a href=\"https://www.buyshared.net/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">BuyShared</a> user, you\u2019re unlikely to become one in the near future.</p><p>@Francisco stated the reason for the change is the high support load that shared hosting generates.&nbsp; This makes sense \u2013 your average VM customer is more sophisticated and self-supporting.&nbsp; If a VM customer runs into an issue with his web server, he\u2019s more likely to search for an answer, ask on forums, query StackExchange, or simply troubleshoot the issue.&nbsp; While some shared hosting customers are pros \u2013 people who just want someone else to deal with the hassle of configuring web services, particularly if they have many users \u2013 many more shared hosters are less technical folk who have little understanding beyond the basics of cPanel.&nbsp; When they load up a couple dozen WordPress plugins or copy/paste instructions they\u2019ve read on the Internet, generating tickets asking why their site is slow or has stopped working quickly eats into thin margins.</p><p>The good news is that judging by @Francisco\u2019s comments, <a href=\"https://www.buyvm.net/\">BuyVM</a> intends to innovate.&nbsp; They\u2019ve been a leader in bringing bigger cloud features to the lowend market, all riding on their in-house panel (Stallion).</p><p>Kudos to <a href=\"https://www.buyvm.net/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">BuyVM</a> for doing this the right way \u2013 simply making <a href=\"https://www.buyshared.net/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">BuyShared</a> products out of stock but continuing to support their users.&nbsp; We\u2019re looking forward to seeing what <a href=\"https://www.buyvm.net/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">BuyVM</a> has in store for 2021 \u2013 <strong>and look for a more in-depth review of their services here on LowEndBox later this month!</strong></p><div class=\"relpost-thumb-wrapper\"><div class=\"relpost-thumb-container\"><h3>Related posts:</h3><div style=\"clear: both\"></div><div style=\"clear: both\"></div><div class=\"relpost-block-container\"><a class=\"relpost-block-single\" href=\"https://lowendbox.com/blog/lowendtalk-2020-best-providers-award-results/\"><div style=\"width: 150px; height: 215px;\"><div class=\"relpost-block-single-image\" alt=\"LowEndTalk 2020 Best Providers Award Results\" style=\"background: transparent url(https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/2020-top-providers-copy-150x150.png) no-repeat scroll 0% 0%; width: 150px; height: 150px;\"></div><div class=\"relpost-block-single-text\" style=\"font-family: Arial;  font-size: 12px;  color: #333333;\">LowEndTalk 2020 Best Providers Award Results</div></div></a><a class=\"relpost-block-single\" href=\"https://lowendbox.com/blog/no-support-linux-hosting-hacked-shuts-down/\"><div style=\"width: 150px; height: 215px;\"><div class=\"relpost-block-single-image\" alt=\"No Support Linux Hosting Hacked, Shuts Down\" style=\"background: transparent url(https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/NoSupportLinuxHosting-150x150.png) n